  "detailed_description": "Twisty Puzzle World contains 400+ twisty / magic puzzles. In addition you can create new puzzles with the ingame editor to give you limitless possibilities.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe editor has many options like: <br />\r\n- choose shape/3d-model/voxel-shape<br />\r\n- choose symmetry (like cube, dodecahedron, icosahedron and dihedral)<br />\r\n- move or rotate the shape<br />\r\n- apply cutting planes<br />\r\n- change colors of the stickers<br />\r\n- apply pictures on the stickers (add your own pictures to any puzzle) <br />\r\n- bandage cubies",
  "about_the_game": "Twisty Puzzle World contains 400+ twisty / magic puzzles. In addition you can create new puzzles with the ingame editor to give you limitless possibilities.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe editor has many options like: <br />\r\n- choose shape/3d-model/voxel-shape<br />\r\n- choose symmetry (like cube, dodecahedron, icosahedron and dihedral)<br />\r\n- move or rotate the shape<br />\r\n- apply cutting planes<br />\r\n- change colors of the stickers<br />\r\n- apply pictures on the stickers (add your own pictures to any puzzle) <br />\r\n- bandage cubies",
